<h2 data-section-id="1fx29ek" data-start="3841" data-end="3877"><span role="text">✔ <code data-start="3846" data-end="3854">app.py</code> (IMPORTANT UI UPGRADE)</span></h2>
<p data-start="3879" data-end="3932">You already did a great job—just enhance it slightly:</p>
